on time management...
===

* meetings should be scheduled in advance (at least 24
  hours).
* all meetings and activities should be scheduled.
  * schedule vacations too!
* have a fixed set number of working hours. allocate them.
  * allocate time for meetings.
  * allocate time for tasks/chores.
  * allocate time for freestyle.
* on crunch time, use some of your freestyle time - but
  don't use it all.
* work on a single task at any moment and do it well.
